## 2. Project Architecture Overview

### High-Level Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Hardware["🔌 Hardware Layer"]
        ESP32["ESP32 Microcontroller"]
        PIR["PIR Motion Sensor"]
        FLAME["Flame Sensor"]
        ULTRASONIC["Ultrasonic Sensor"]
        RELAY["4-Channel Relay"]
        PZEM["Voltage/Current Sensor"]
    end

    subgraph Cloud["☁️ Cloud Layer"]
        RTDB["Firebase Realtime Database"]
        AUTH["Firebase Authentication"]
        FCM["Firebase Cloud Messaging"]
    end

    subgraph Frontend["💻 Frontend Layer"]
        REACT["React + TypeScript App"]
        HOOKS["Custom Hooks"]
        COMPONENTS["Dashboard Components"]
    end

    subgraph AI["🤖 AI Layer"]
        OLLAMA["Ollama LLM"]
        PROXY["Python Proxy Server"]
    end

    ESP32 --> RTDB
    RTDB --> ESP32
    REACT --> RTDB
    REACT --> AUTH
    REACT --> FCM
    REACT --> PROXY
    PROXY --> OLLAMA
    PIR --> ESP32
    FLAME --> ESP32
    ULTRASONIC --> ESP32
    PZEM --> ESP32
    ESP32 --> RELAY
```

### Data Flow

1. **Sensors → ESP32** → Data collected every 2 seconds
2. **ESP32 → Firebase RTDB** → Data pushed to cloud
3. **Firebase RTDB → React App** → Real-time listeners update UI
4. **React App → Firebase RTDB** → User commands sent to ESP32
5. **React App → Ollama** → Natural language processing
6. **Ollama → React App** → AI responses displayed

